        </item>
        <item>
            <title>傳微博實施前台實名制　粉絲多於 50 萬需公開真名字＋性別</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/weibo/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=weibo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/weibo/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 07:50:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[實名制]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微博]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[自媒體]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199527</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日有消息指，微博計劃向粉絲人數多於 50 萬的自媒體實施前台實名制。若然消息屬實，微博將成為首個實施前台實名制的社交平台。</p><p>中國知名財經博主、上海浦東工商聯副主席洪榕上週五（13 日）在微博發文，指全網自媒體要實施前台實名制，粉絲人數多於 50 萬的用戶真名要在一級頁前端展示。粉絲可以知道自己關注的自媒體究竟是男是女，是現實中的誰了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.19.05.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.19.05-694x241.png" alt="" width="694" height="241" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.19.05-694x241.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.19.05-768x267.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.19.05.png 1260w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>洪榕隨後補充，多於 100 萬名粉絲的自媒體帳號需於 10 月底前於前台展示真實姓名，多於 50 萬名的需於 12 月底前展示，而多於 10 萬名的則只需在後台完成身份實名認證並於前台展示職業資料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.10.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.10-694x217.png" alt="" width="694" height="217" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.10-694x217.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.10-1280x401.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.10-768x241.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.10.png 1436w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>消息一出，各大知名博主紛紛表示洪榕的消息屬實。科技博主拆台 CT 轉發洪榕的微博並稱，微博曾向他徵求意見，目前限定的範圍是娛樂 、社會和財經，更指除微博外亦有其他大型社交平台向他徵求類似意見。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.39.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.39-404x580.png" alt="" width="404" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.39-404x580.png 404w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.39-626x900.png 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-16-07.57.39.png 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 404px" /></a></p><p>圖片來源：電玩幫、微博</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.vgover.com/news/61952">電玩幫</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
