            <title>僅處理器升級，三款 iPad 傳本週推出新版</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/apple-to-announce-new-ipad-models-this-week-featuring-upgraded-chips/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-to-announce-new-ipad-models-this-week-featuring-upgraded-chips</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/apple-to-announce-new-ipad-models-this-week-featuring-upgraded-chips/notebook/tablet-notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美鳳]]>
